snippet.title: Amber Heard Lands A Role In NEW AVENGERS Movie 2022…!? (Johnny Reacts)
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Lands A Role In NEW AVENGERS Movie 2022…!? (Johnny Reacts)
One of the biggest "side effects" if you will about the court case between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp is that both of them are facing certain issues in regards to casting. Because while both of them have technically had roles during their time in court, it's also true that many studios have either distanced themselves from the couple, or, are just refusing to work with them at all. While Amber Heard is having a big role coming up with Aquaman 2, outside of that...there's not much. However, a rumor is stating that she might be heading to another superhero universe soon... We'll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have it, everyone! A look at the situation between Amber Heard and Marvel Studios and whether she might honestly be considered for the role of Susan Storm, or just an MCU role in general. Do you want Amber Heard anywhere near the Fantastic For or the Marvel Cinematic Universe? Do you think that these rumors about what'll happen to her are getting out of hand? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
